{"tid":1407503,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[極重要]聽日想被罷工嘅入一入黎","createTime":"2019-08-04T15:32:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T02:32:48.000Z","uid":297967,"like":158,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"8b0fd9f5f647dc458eee97971d0ed9b615ce07e1","tid":1407503,"uid":297967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:32:17.000Z","msg":"相信各位打工仔都好想被罷工 好想聽朝大大聲同老細講因為交通問題而翻唔到工<br />\n若果每一個人都係咁諗 但乜都唔做 根本係 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇用</span></span><br />\n你地嘅諗法： 想企係地鐵站/巴士站等極都等唔到車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&mdash;＞同老細講翻唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事實係要：一齊早起身幫手落自己區視察交通<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />＞冇車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />＞翻唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果個個都想坐享其成 乜都唔做 想有人幫你做埋你果份 呢件事冇可能成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講真，多你一個，對成件事真係好好多<br />\nBTW , 有冇人有聽日嘅流程?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34138b9fd4c4f1e33550ebdd03a75a7de0bb61c7","tid":1407503,"uid":25573,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:32:47.000Z","msg":"自己交通自己塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f9da64b72a40b2d678503170992cf92cc888cad","tid":1407503,"uid":175451,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:34:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8afec285bfb8b6b88d9308bc296cd11fbe0a734e","tid":1407503,"uid":297967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:34:14.000Z","msg":"有冇人知聽日要點?"},{"pid":"190829b39044988c4330a1ea473bd446fc53fb2d","tid":1407503,"uid":39568,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:34:37.000Z"